程序包 cn.seu.edu.InfoView

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    InfoInsertView
    This class creates a frame, which is used to add new students and teachers by the information manager.
    InfoNewStuView
    This class creates a frame, which shows some student's existent information, and is used to complete student's information by herself or himself.
    InfoNewTchView
    This class creates a frame, which shows some teacher's existent information, and is used to complete teacher's information by herself or himself.
    InfoOutputAllView
    This class creates a frame, which shows all students' existent information.
    InfoQueryView
    This class creates a frame, which includes five query condition to find eligible students.
    InfoStuView
    This class creates a frame, which shows entered student's all existent information.
    InfoTchView
    This class creates a frame, which shows entered teacher's all existent information.
